Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:48.61,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:57.63,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  So you've been deployed to Mistral, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:00:59.03,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:03.46,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,But supposedly the food's good and there's no shortage of beautiful women.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:06.63,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been almost half a year since the armistice was declared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:09.80,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,It's a relief that we've survived this long!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:13.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Look!  Grim Bourlouge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:14.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Maaaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:17.65,SoRaNoWoTo-Alt,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,What?  That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.99,0:01:17.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Not again!  Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:20.62,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You up, little missy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:24.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your share of the spoils.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:27.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Caramel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:32.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you so much for giving me something so expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:35.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Sergeant, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:41.24,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Sergeant,0000,0000,0000,,What's that for?  Rumor goes if you treat the trumpeter good, you'll hear the retreat signals better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:45.36,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare to see a new recruit, with the draft being over and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.36,0:01:46.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Were you a volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.35,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!  I wanted to learn how to play music—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:50.33,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:52.57,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:55.99,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,At least you're honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:56.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Alt,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:57.58,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with that, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:59.55,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Private Second Class, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:00.78,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:03.31,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Sorami Kanata, at your service!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:16.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's a festival in Seize today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:19.57,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So I can only take you this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.58,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Look there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:31.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's where you've been assigned to.  It's called the Time-Heralding Bastion{Tellng Fortress}.{Official change after much belaboring. No changey. ~Sumi}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.29,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your sights on that and follow the roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,"Notice of personnel change.  Private Second Class, Sorami Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:45.82,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You are assigned to Platoon 1121, Seize, Trois Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:49.11,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Signed, Helvetia Republic Army Command Headquarters."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,1320 hours, mission completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:05.13,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:19.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,The city of lakes and glass... Seize!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.43,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Check-in time is at 1500 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.56,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally let you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:36.58,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Direction check, confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Check-in time, confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment check, confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Forward... march!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.36,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,G-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.92,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're fish figurines!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,10 and 25 sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:40.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretty doll th—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.11,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.16,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:52.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,A kitten excited by the festival just went scampering off any which way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.39,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no helping that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.39,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Kittens are inherently meandering creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:00.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what makes them cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:05.37,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be fine if it were a stray,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,but unfortunately, that one was more of a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.56,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,She startled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:35.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But I found another wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.15,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.36,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,A girl from the bastion{fortress}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:01.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Male,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the helping with the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.57,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Voices,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Voices,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:24.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.50,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you back for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.21,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Take...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.61,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,To you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:57.98,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.45,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Getting involved in all of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do about that uniform?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.97,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Um... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.34,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:15.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Tha—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.87,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:36.73,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Is the temperature okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:38.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!  It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:41.08,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:44.03,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,You made such an easy mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.60,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have just kept clear of the shots?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:52.27,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?  This sort of dye will wash out easily once it's dried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.60,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,That... was a part of the festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:59.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,It's connected to a legend of Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,A legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:08.39,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,About the maidens of fire... who protect this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.20,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, there's more work now, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.53,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:24.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Those repairs you requested were completed, also.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.27,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,The repairs on this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Phylicia, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.07,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,That meddling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:41.58,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Late, late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.99,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Laaaate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:46.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,And after we came all the way out here to pick her up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:49.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.  Let's wait calmly, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:54.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,It was a gift from your father, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:55.67,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice article.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:58.88,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:03.21,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:07.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always getting lost somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:10.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,but thanks to that, I was able to have such a wonderful encounter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.07,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Think nothing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.35,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Still, do your best to not get lost around here, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:16.26,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:23.67,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.34,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,You can... interpret sounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:41.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,This has a very calming tone that's somehow nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,You thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:47.43,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:57.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,You really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:01.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Were you going to die for something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:02.59,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:06.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:10.16,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine... I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:17.31,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:23.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:44.11,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0025,,I've something to take care of, so I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.92,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0025,,Don't get lost anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.18,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0025,,That bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.56,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0025,,I'm sure it was something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0025,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:12:59.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.30,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,That direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.31,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Forward march!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,The fire maidens?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.63,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:22.50,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Long before the world became what it is today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:30.11,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,In the valleys of this city, there lived a winged demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:37.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,The demon breathed fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:37.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,shook the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.57,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,and wrought pain amongst the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:48.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, it kidnapped the maidens living in the bastion{fortress},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:51.76,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,and trapped them in an underground labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:02.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, the maidens refused to give in,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:07.15,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,and used golden horns granted unto them by angels to call out to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.45,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Once escaping from the maze,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:13.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,they borrowed strength from a great spider,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:18.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,and vanquished the demon, severing its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:23.98,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,When they did so, it began to spew forth flames violently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:28.69,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Had it continued unchecked, the town above would have undoubtedly been engulfed entirely in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:37.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,In order to contain the belching flames, one by one the maidens embraced the demon's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:43.92,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx98}Each day, the citizens would pour water onto the fading flames surrounding the demon's head and the maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:47.67,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,815)}The fire burned for an entire year before it was finally extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:52.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Every year since, in order to soothe the spirits of those maidens who rescued the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:56.34,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,the water-pouring festival has been held.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:53.59,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Seems she didn't make it after all... that new girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:55.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,What's it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:58.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Captain, it's Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.20,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.24,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,That role really suits her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:05.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,What a great idea it was to have her do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.65,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't we draw lots—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten myself lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:21.74,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a good-for-nothing, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:33.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes being lost can lead to fun situations too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:39.57,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,that's usually because you meet someone you didn't know before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:45.58,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want... to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:51.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  I want to find my mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:52.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:59.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you wish, then that's the feeling that will be conducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:01.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:03.85,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds will always resonate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:06.48,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Will always resonate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:09.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1014)}Always resonate and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:13.39,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And so, be conducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:18.34,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Fire maidens, may you rest here in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:22.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,We beg you to embrace the demon, placate its curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:26.16,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,so that it may never again awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:27.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:29.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,A golden horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.53,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Has the demon—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:32.95,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,You think it's awakened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.60,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Extend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:49.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... please hear my sounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.78,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It reached someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:10.65,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds resonate, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:17.57,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Private Second Class, Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.50,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Where am...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:27.87,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Going to stay half-asleep the whole night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:32.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This is the garrison of Platoon 1121, the Time-Heralding Bastion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:51.48,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,About yesterday... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.33,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry for causing you trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:55.59,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,You really did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.27,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I-I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:19:59.09,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:00.79,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,I was kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.87,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,However, reckless actions are forbidden from here out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,For just a small bell like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:29.72,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.61,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,The trumpet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:36.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,...why this fortress is called the Time-Heralding Bastion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.52,SoRaNoWoTo-Thoughts,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,The sounds of the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:49.95,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Kazumiya Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:53.06,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,That's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:56.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be guiding you in becoming a trumpeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:02.22,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working with you, Sergeant Major Rio, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:03.76,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Just Rio is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:03.76,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:05.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,That's Phylicia's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:08.76,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Captain's policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.29,0:22:10.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,There's no rank or class here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:12.05,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:20.13,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's get off to a rolling start, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:21.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear a wake-up call!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,The girl this time is pretty bad, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.85,0:24:26.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Grandma,0000,0000,0140,,Next time, First Battle: The Story of the Chair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:38.87,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Aimerais-tu en chantant voir quelque chose se passer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:38.87,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Would you like to see something develop as you sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:46.08,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Et que l'air soit plus pur, les cœurs des hommes transformés?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:46.08,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}For the air to be more pure, to see the hearts of men transformed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:53.22,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Et pourtant tout est si fragile ici sur la Terre.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:53.22,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Yet everything is so fragile here on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:14:00.01,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Il n'est rien qui soit futile, tu sais.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:14:00.01,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Nothing is without reason, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:18.17,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}D'un côté au bout et quelques fois pour tes yeux,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:18.17,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}In the end, only sometimes is reality mirrored in your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:25.19,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}et de l'autre les pauvres et bien souvent monstrueux.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:25.19,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}and at others in those of the wretched and often very demonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:30.66,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Qu'importe ce que ton coeur te dira,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:30.66,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}No matter what side you hear being told,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:37.77,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}souviens-toi que la différence n'est que dans tes yeux.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:37.77,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}remember that the difference is only in your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:46.44,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Chantons toutes les couleurs du monde,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:46.44,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Let's sing all the colors of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:53.85,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}sans manquer une couleur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:53.85,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}without forgetting a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:15:00.07,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Chaque chose a sa place ici,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:15:00.07,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Everything has a place here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:10.27,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}chaque étoile dans la symphonie de notre vie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:10.27,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}like every star in the symphony of our life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:22.11,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Chaque humain nous dit du ciel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:22.11,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Every human makes sounds of the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:29.17,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Chaque tout était cintré,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:29.17,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Everything is tightly bound,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:35.32,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}et quand on se voit aussi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:35.32,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}and when we see each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:42.49,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}pour nous monter dans les étoiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:42.49,French-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}we'll be taken to the stars.
